title: My Art Journey
script:
Anushka: Namaste dosto! Aaj main aap sabhi se apni kala yatra ke baare mein baat karna chahti hoon.
Anushka: Yaad hai bachpan mein, rangon se kitna pyaar tha? Har deewar canvas lagti thi!
Anushka: Dheere dheere, woh pyaar ek junoon ban gaya.
Anushka: Kai baar laga, 'yeh kya kar rahi hoon?'... par dil mein woh aag bujhi nahi.
Anushka: Fir maine socha, kyun na ise hi zindagi bana loon?
Anushka: Aur bas, wahi se shuru hui meri asli journey.
Anushka: Abhi toh bahut kuch seekhna hai, bahut aage jaana hai.
Anushka: Par har rang, har brushstroke, mujhe ek nayi kahani sunata hai.
Anushka: Umeed hai, aap bhi apni passion ko follow karein.
Anushka: Dhanyavaad!
